@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ocxume(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.cos(tmp)
    v1 = (wp.abs(wp.abs(tmp + 0.49)) - wp.sin(v0))
    tmp = 0.06
    v2 = wp.exp(wp.sin((v1 + 0.94 + v2 + 0.58)))
    v0 = (0.75 / ((v0 + 0.97 * v0 + 0.15) - (v2 + 0.68 * v0 + 0.05)))
    v2 = v0
    v2 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
